            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報22680點，跌247點，較上日現貨收市價22944點低水264點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5603點，跌67點，低水69點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8375點，跌86點，低水88點。</p>\n</div>",
