            "title": "DeepSeek稱融資消息屬謠言",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地傳媒《騰訊科技》引述DeepSeek相關人士澄清指，融資消息均為謠言。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250213_CH_deepseek-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250213_CH_deepseek-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技媒體The Information引述消息指出，內地人工智能(AI)模型初創公司DeepSeek成立2年來，首次考慮向外集資，由於其AI模型大受歡迎，因而要增加資源投放以滿足明顯增加的需求，所以促成內部討論引入更多投資者。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市傳阿里巴巴(09988)和國有基金已表示有意參與是次投資。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14719414-deepseek%e7%a8%b1%e8%9e%8d%e8%b3%87%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af%e5%b1%ac%e8%ac%a0%e8%a8%80",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/02/20250111_GL_source-ap_DeepSeek.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 09:15:54",
